name: Combat_Go-Go_Dress
description:
Unique!
Worn once, Made by me :)
Size 10 but would fit an 8 too. Made from a cotton blend I think – Halter dress with a circle skirt attached, Looks fab with a net petticoat underneath – The dress has corseting up the front of the dress – black silk ribbon – Zip up the back.
Please don’t hesitate to contact me if you need any more details.

name: TUK_Black&White_Shoes
description: Brand New Gorgeous Black & White Slingback Peekaboo Shoes. They are brand new, sadly they don’t fit me. They’ve sat in my wardrobe for a few months and I’m finally having to part with them. No point in having shoes just to look at is there :( So, upside is, one of you lucky people get to have and adore them! Perfect present for Christmas! They’re marked a US 7 which I believe is a UK4. They are a beautiful pair of black and white patent shoes with a slight platform. There’s a slight peep-toe and the heel (from the back of the shoe) measures 4”. They will be posted in a TUK box and wrapped in tissue paper inside. The black is patent not matte
